    "Cannot %@ because iCloud is unavailable. Changes are paused to keep your history consistent.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "无法%@，因为 iCloud 不可用。更改已暂停，以保持历史记录一致。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Cannot %@ until you relaunch HistoryLib to apply the iCloud Sync change. History changes are blocked until then so on-device data does not diverge.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在重新启动 HistoryLib 应用 iCloud 同步更改之前，无法%@。在此之前历史更改将被阻止，以免设备上的数据发生分歧。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
